package.name: opOpenSocialPlugin
package.notes:
Bug (バグ):
#1827: [pc][mobile] Fatal error in application/invite when a member has no friend. #1844: [mobile] Container doesn't send a location header when an external server sent a location header #1845: [pc] "home" view doesn't exists #1846: [pc] opCacheStrageFile doesn't create cache correctly. #1847: [pc] opShindigRemoteContentFetcher doesn't send header correctly set #1848: [pc] Gadget's cache isn't deleted at the update of an application #1876: [api] PHP Notice in "lib_for_shindig/OpenPNEService.php " #1899: [pc] /application/inviteのレスポンスを修正する #1906: [pc] Fix a mistake of the relayUrl in gadget component #1907: [pc] 招待完了時に正しいレスポンスが返されない #1933: [etc] opOpenSocial:execute-lifecycle-event タスクの limit-request オプションで指定した値を守らない場合がある #1934: [api] PersistentAPI doesn't return all key-value pair #1965: [pc] gadgets.container._parseIframeUrl doesn't return first parameter correctly. #1988: [pc] modalboxを2回目以降に表示すると、読み込みが完了するまで前回表示時の内容が残ってしまう #2065: [api] opOpenSocialProfileExport doesn't return birthday when public flag of birthday is '3' and owner is viewer
Enhancement (機能追加・改善):
#1849: [etc] Change class name of "opCacheStrageFile" to "opShindigCacheStrageFile" #1866: [api] Change the demiliter of "date of birth" to "-" from "/" #1868: [etc] Add ability to relay notice of limited invalidation back to outside Shindig #1935: [test] opOpenSocial:execute-lifecycle-event タスクのテストを追加 #1954: [task] opOpenSocial:execute-lifecycle-event のメモリ使用量削減等に関する改善 #1964: [test] Add unit-test for container.js #1979: [api] ヘルパーを使用せずにプロフィールURLの生成を行う #2052: [test] Add unit-test for the class opOpenSocialProfileExportTest

release.notes: Fixed some security hole and changed base language from Japanese to English on the pc_frontend.
Added an ability to render iframes of the outer OpenSocial container and fixed the PersistentAPI.
This version is compatible with Doctrine.
The preseted profile item was made to correspond to API
Fixed MemberApplicationSetting model, because index key is too long.
Added an ability for Albums API.
Added an ability to approve install of the app from SNS admin.
Added Activity API and an ability to request share app.
Add an ability for the lifecycle-event.
Fixed some bug on the mobile.
Supported location service, and added an ability to extend url of replacing on the mobile.
